  "prompt": "Fellow bad people on Quora, what kind of question will it take to talk about your bad tendencies?",
  "response": "It seems you're looking to spark an honest conversation about behaviors or tendencies that might be considered \"bad.\" A question that could elicit such discussions might be:\n\n\"What are some of your guilty pleasures or habits that you know are not great, but you indulge in anyway?\"\n\nThis kind of question invites people to reflect on their behaviors without judgment and can lead to a more open dialogue about the complexities of human nature. Remember, everyone has their flaws, and discussing them can often lead to understanding and growth.",
